#: ../../talk/webinar.rst:3
msgid "Webinar and lobby"
msgstr "Seimineár Gréasáin agus stocaireacht"

#: ../../talk/webinar.rst:5
msgid ""
"The lobby feature allows you to show guests a waiting screen until the call "
"starts. This is ideal for webinars with external participants, for example."
msgstr ""
"Leis an ngné stocaireachta, is féidir leat scáileán feithimh a thaispeáint "
"d’aíonna go dtí go dtosaíonn an glao. Tá sé seo iontach maith do sheimineáir"
" ghréasáin le rannpháirtithe seachtracha, mar shampla."

#: ../../talk/webinar.rst:10
msgid ""
"You can choose to let the participants join the call at a specific time, or "
"when you dismiss the lobby manually."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat ligean do na rannpháirtithe páirt a ghlacadh sa ghlao ag am "
"ar leith, nó nuair a dhúnann tú an stocaireacht de láimh."

#: ../../talk/webinar.rst:12
msgid ""
"You can configure the lobby in ``Conversation settings`` under the "
"``Webinar`` section."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat an stocaireacht a chumrú i ``Socruithe comhrá`` faoin rannán "
"``Seimineár Gréasáin``."
